HEADWORD: Unrivet
<hw>Un*riv"et</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>rivet</ets>.]</ety> <def>To take out, or loose,
the rivets of; <as>as, to <ex>unrivet</ex> boiler plates</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
